snippet.title: Camera Panda
snippet.description:
CameraPanda.com is proud to present Brandon Sanderson's creative writing lecture series, taught winter semester of 2016 at BYU. The videos were filmed by SkepteonMedia.

If you love, love, love the videos you are more than welcome to say thanks in one or more of the following ways

 - go buy a camera or lens at http://CameraPanda.com
 - buy something at Amazon through one of our affiliate links, like http://amzn.to/29C4CFG. If you visit that link and then buy anything else (like even a snowblower), we still get credit
 - link your awesome site to http://camerapanda.com
 - add a CameraPanda.com / Earl Cahill acknowledgement in your eventual best seller, which was at least partially aided / inspired by this series
 - nominate the series for a Best Related Work Hugo award
 - say thanks in the comments
 - just enjoy

CameraPanda.com, LLC and Skepteon Media, LLC are owned and operated by Earl Cahill.

Thanks to all and enjoy!
Earl
